    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c6845f204b53cc7450e4616"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "<i>Perkele</i>, you need to do some explaining first if you want us to get back and face those monsters again.\n\nHow is even possible to pilot a BattleMech without a [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreNeuroHelmet],neurohelmet]] to provide balance to the gyro?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 3,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c7d585a3941007ebb7274e2"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f36230355c1800006a",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cafda50346ccd1f8e272a7f"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "After decades of research Apple managed to create an artificial microprocessor dedicated solely to managing the BattleMech's balance.\n\nThe downside is that it occupies the entire cockpit and it can only be equipped on 'Mechs of Assault class and we also had to remove several tons of armor for weight issues.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 4,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c261080345c5e7cb3d774bd"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": {
        "id": "AppleComputersInterstellarLeaderDefault"
      },
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c6b5eb52fdb62f4c9194dad"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "That does not explain all that we saw, your Grace.\n\nSeveral [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreIndustrialMech],IndustrialMechs]] are already automated for specific tasks and can operate remotely without the need for neurohelmets or even pilots.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 5,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c34048acf62c1c8fb9e96bc"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c1c118ccd8c7da3a4ba6761"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "But what we saw back there was not automated [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAgroMech],AgroMechs]] picking up grain from fields.\n\nWhatever was piloting these [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreBattleMech],'Mechs]], it knew tactics and coordination to ambush us.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c21f4f9f92de58673f65c05"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f26230355c18000069",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c7da26ad2d30e707aaad0dd"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "As I previously said, we can't trust your company with that kind of information.\n\nNow, you need to return to the planet and destroy the main research base... ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Excuse me, your Grace, but I believed we have already fulfilled our contract. XO?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c3f404113ac90a157494abd"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": {
        "id": "AppleComputersInterstellarLeaderDefault"
      },
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c3d27683b0f5935875d1134"
      },
      "index": 7,
      "text": "That is correct, Commander {COMMANDER.LastName}.\n\nOur contract specified a site recovery and we have completed it, so according to [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMercenaryReviewBoard],MRB]] we are free to depart and collect our pay.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 8,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c6223b3296f266d3cc30eb5"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f26230355c18000069",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c82e50855c5787c3f9f98f9"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "You... you mercenaries don't actually believe you and your 'Mechs can  just run and hide under contract regulations, do you?\n\nBecause the moment your DropShip starts leaving orbit, is when I hire all the bounty hunters in the Periphery after you and Prince Davion might even set the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMIIO],MIIO]] and his [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreRabidFoxes],Rabid Foxes]] after you!",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 9,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cbf9ff5feea36654332967e"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": {
        "id": "AppleComputersInterstellarLeaderDefault"
      },
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c76d1b075bf142ad2346c34"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Your Grace, we can't properly defeat these 'Mechs unless you reveal to us what is their origin and abilities.\n\nAnd since we are renegotiating a new contract, we consider this to be crucial information for operational security.\n",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "And you already want the technology destroyed, so who will believe mercenaries like us?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 10,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cf6f054a33a6f416cb0d0ce"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f26230355c18000069",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c54590376d5bde659875e6e"
      },
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Very well, since the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreStarLeague],Star League]] we have been working on computer solutions for the issues of depending on MechWarriors to pilot BattleMechs and their unreliability to follow orders.\n\nHowever, our research into artificial intelligence was not well received initially because of the social changes it would imply to replace an entire warrior caste and declare them obsolete.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 11,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c8805fadce60c40e5536806"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": {
        "id": "AppleComputersInterstellarLeaderDefault"
      },
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c346c2479812bddb360c2db"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "However, the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSuccessionWars],Succession Wars]] changed that paradigm - we now live in a time of 'Mech scarcity, and a single lance can conquer an entire planet.\n\nAnd the ability of control and coordinate efficiently lances, companies or even greater numbers of military units multiplies even further their combat value.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 12,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c5394815ad3a03ab97a1c59"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": {
        "id": "AppleComputersInterstellarLeaderDefault"
      },
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
