    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cd166619c2c788a1ef367c8"
      },
      "index": 12,
      "text": "However, while the software requirements to remotely control a group of 'Mechs could be solved out by our engineers, we were missing a key element until we had a breakthrough.\n\nHave any of you ever heard of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSpaceDefenseSystem],Casper SDS]] system?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 13,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c48c7019f7e89428b85b37c"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": {
        "id": "AppleComputersInterstellarLeaderDefault"
      },
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": {
        "ops": [
          {
            "functionName": "Set BattleTech Camera Lock",
            "args": [
              {
                "int_value": 0,
                "bool_value": false,
                "float_value": 0.0,
                "string_value": "AUTO",
                "call_value": null,
                "variableref_value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cf942ddc13ddf00a1d95a0d"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Yes, your Grace, I studied it at the academy, it was a series of automated drones that was used during the Star League to protect high-value systems like [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTerra],Terra]].\n\nYou were able to replicate the system?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 14,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c968af1565787f9e57c221b"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3a06230355c18000067",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c0a53f137f278acaf99ee79"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Partially, we already had gained access to the schematics possessed by [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreNirasakiComputersCollective],Nirasaki Computers Collective]] but once the Combine found out about our interest in [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreNirasaki],Nirasaki]], our operatives had to leave the planet.\n\nBut the real breakthrough was with the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreFedComAccords],FedCom Accords]] which gave us access to the models made by the original designer, [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreUlsopRobotics],Ultrop Robotics]], since they used to have an office at [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTharkad],Tharkad]].",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 15,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cc0d949e9c93fdfd1083d34"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": {
        "id": "AppleComputersInterstellarLeaderDefault"
      },
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cbff1388becac108a0f1c85"
      },
      "index": 15,
      "text": "So what do you think happened on the planet, Duke Roberts?\n\nYour AI model became self-aware and ordered the 'Mechs to kill all humans?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 16,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c9daa46a74c15b9a7bd6347"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c6f6e54edf24e16d236060f"
      },
      "index": 16,
      "text": "We gave it strict parameters and guardrails, the AI agent piloting the drones was guaranteed to follow orders unless it was sabotaged...\n\nIt does not matter, this project must be completely eliminated because we can't risk bringing back any compromised systems.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "{COMPANY.CompanyName} right here at your disposal, your Grace.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 17,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c5551313a6d0c388be9601e"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": {
        "id": "AppleComputersInterstellarLeaderDefault"
      },
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c7a84b8de919c7ed0e059ee"
      },
      "index": 17,
      "text": "We certainly can do it, as the Commander says, for the right price, Duke Roberts.\n\nBut we would like as payment the <i>Dark Horse</i> that we returned to Apple Computers, as you previously requested to us.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 18,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
